#: krandrmodule.cpp:100
msgid ""
"The screen whose settings you would like to change can be selected using this "
"drop-down list."
msgstr ""
"Gellir ddewis y sgrîn y dymunwch newid y gosodiadau ohono gan ddefnyddio'r "
"llam-restr."

#: krandrmodule.cpp:109
